cpufreqd (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low
  
  * New Upstream (closes: #268020)
  * Added support for extended /proc/stat in 2.6 kernels (closes: #264126)
  * Added translation from percentage to absolute values for 2.6 kernels
    (closes: #254418)
  * Implemented checks for empty configurations and supplied defaults values
    for the general section (closes: #243649)
  * Removed frequencies translation in postinst as now percentages are
    supported for both 2.4 and 2.6 kernels.

